c: 6
v: 36
t: "'inma yjybk -ayha alrswl- 'iilaa ma daeawt 'iilayh min alhudaa aladhin yasmaeun alkalam smae qbwl. 'amaa alkufaar fahum fi eidad almwta; li'ana alhayat alhaqiqiat 'iinama takun bal'islam. walmwta yukhrijuhum allah min qbwrhm ahya', thuma yaeudun 'iilayh yawm alqiamat lywfu hisabuhum wjza'hm"